quran[15]{c,v,t}:
  23,75,"Walaw rahimnahum wakashafnama bihim min durrin lalajjoo fee tughyanihimyaAAmahoon"
  23,76,"Walaqad akhathnahum bilAAathabifama istakanoo lirabbihim wama yatadarraAAoon"
  23,77,"Hatta itha fatahnaAAalayhim baban tha AAathabin shadeedin ithahum feehi mublisoon"
  23,78,"Wahuwa allathee anshaa lakumu assamAAawal-absara wal-af-idata qaleelan matashkuroon"
  23,79,"Wahuwa allathee tharaakum feeal-ardi wa-ilayhi tuhsharoon"
  23,80,"Wahuwa allathee yuhyeewayumeetu walahu ikhtilafu allayli wannahariafala taAAqiloon"
  23,81,"Bal qaloo mithla ma qalaal-awwaloon"
  23,82,"Qaloo a-itha mitnawakunna turaban waAAithamana-inna lamabAAoothoon"
  23,83,"Laqad wuAAidna nahnu waabaonahatha min qablu in hatha illa asateerual-awwaleen"
  23,84,"Qul limani al-ardu waman feehain kuntum taAAlamoon"
  23,85,"Sayaqooloona lillahi qul afalatathakkaroon"
  23,86,"Qul man rabbu assamawatiassabAAi warabbu alAAarshi alAAatheem"
  23,87,"Sayaqooloona lillahi qul afalatattaqoon"
  23,88,"Qul man biyadihi malakootu kulli shay-inwahuwa yujeeru wala yujaru AAalayhi in kuntumtaAAlamoon"
  23,89,"Sayaqooloona lillahi qul faannatusharoon"
